column5: Here I am doing some paperwork and decided to take a break and WOW look at all of the people here. So what are you supposed to be doing now? I should be plumbing but the weather is just down right nasty.   Have a good rainey day.  Art
I should be fishing. Hmm what's stopping me? Guess I'm going fishing!
retired for two weeks now can do anything I want    to wet to go fishing so here I am.  vance
I'm working ...just surf the OFC between calls.
Gotta love these things called days off  , and it's too wet to do much else...  Maureen
they make me work at a computer part of the day and some forms I have to fill out are on line...some how this is the website that pops up when I start my browser.....so what can I do

Im on my days off and my wife has a list of things for me to be getting on with while she's at work.  Mainly install a new floor, paint the walls, and install a new mantle in the master bedroom.  Started to do all that and noticed the roof leaking.  Went up there fixed that and decided that Ive had enough.  So I'm back on the computer until about 5 minutes before she gets home!!  Shhhhhh dont tell!!!
How am I expected to get anything done at work with all these new posts???  I only come to the office for the high-speed internet connection....lol  dk
